1.0.name: wordpress/woocommerce-bitpay
1.0.description:
Add BitPay gateway to WooCommerce

WooCommerce BitPay is a Bitcoin payment gateway for WooCommerce.

Please notice that WooCommerce must be installed and actived.

The WooCommerce BitPay plugin was developed without any incentive from BitPay. None of the plugin developer has ties to this company.

Contribute

You can contribute to the source code in our GitHub page.
